ces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a3c0636be39398d4070943af5599eef106e91ea","tid":947954,"uid":63735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7b4dbb1c2c788b7271123f8f481b0127ef51883","tid":947954,"uid":186297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T16:22:39.000Z","msg":"估唔到連登有人睇呢d片<br />\n前幾日睇咗，導演問答環節解釋得好好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T16:34:01.000Z","msg":"同場，映後談質素（尤其葉七城問的那條，語帶哽咽）不比電影本身遜色。<br />\n<br />\n個人認為《自由行》是暫時應亮老師最佳作品，聰明的遊離於「流亡者自傳」和「自由之鄉旅者」之間，若剛若柔的平衡很精準，從個人、家庭以至地域文化角力，到後設思考導演個人創作，最後提問觀者（不論是有沒有投身創作）對自由與創作取向的空間，整個文本結構和走向的合成在當代華語電影中非常罕見。<br />\n<br />\n唯有希望各位影評大佬前輩不要以墮性思考草草放過這片，《自由行》絕不只値得從獵奇筆墨的介紹"},{"pid":"6873f0d206f8e65742765720a5c92f75584f4b4e","tid":947954,"uid":63735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9512bf6546acdceee3430edaa0719dd122fdebb8","tid":947954,"uid":47983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T16:25:28.000Z","msg":"釜山電影節嘅時候睇咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n撞正啱啱宣布明日大嶼<br />\n邊睇邊忍唔住流眼淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T16:35:12.000Z","msg":"個陣有無播埋《媽媽的口供》？"},{"pid":"5a8a545924382f7dc319018fa1903c0722d4c18b","tid":947954,"uid":47983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6873f0d206f8e65742765720a5c92f75584f4b4e","tid":947954,"uid":63735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9512bf6546acdceee3430edaa0719dd122fdebb8","tid":947954,"uid":47983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T16:25:28.000Z","msg":"釜山電影節嘅時候睇咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br /